       "Yay... I'm invisible again..."  He looks at Devil Gigatron and 
AzureBlade numb to their argument.  "AH why the hell does Devil Gigatron keep 
referring to Devil Gigatron in the bloody third person.  Is Devil Gigatron 
conceited or just plain stupid?  And why won't any moronic Maximal here ever 
acknowledge my existence for more than ten seconds!?"
